{"tid":1490589,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"收到Facebook既新聞稿-大量五毛專頁中國政府有關","createTime":"2019-08-20T07:03:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T07:28:59.000Z","uid":302596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cfce27c68cd692115bdd89ff5df750c0f0db212b","tid":1490589,"uid":302596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:03:08.000Z","msg":"FB - 移除來自中國的有組織非真實散佈行為<br />\n<br />\n香港&ndash;2019年8月20日&ndash; Facebook 今天移除了7個專頁、3個群組和5個帳戶。這些專頁、群組和帳戶均來自一個中國的小型網絡組織，並牽涉參與針對香港的有組織非真實散佈行為。參與這些行動的人士涉及若干造假行為，包括以虛假帳戶（其中一些帳戶已被Facebook自動檢測系統停止使用）管理假冒新聞機構的專頁、在不同群組中刊登帖文、散佈內容，以及驅使用戶前往Facebook 平台以外的新聞網站。有關行動人士經常刊登與政治相關的新聞，包括近期香港示威遊行的話題。雖然執行這些行動的人士嘗試隱藏他們的身分，但Facebook的調查結果顯示這些人士與中國政府有關。<br />\n<br />\n&bull; Facebook 平台上的情況： 5個 Facebook 帳戶、7個專頁和3個群組<br />\n&bull; 追蹤人數：約 15,500個帳戶追蹤一個或多個這些專頁，約2,200個帳戶加入至少這些群組中的其中一個<br />\n<br />\nFacebook根據Twitter提供有關人士在Twitter平台上的異常活動資訊，於Facebook平台上就懷疑有組織非真實散佈行為進行調查，並發現了相關活動。Facebook將繼續監察平台上違反政策的行為，如發現其他違規行為，我們亦會採取相應行動。Facebook已經與執法機構和業界合作夥伴分享有關分析。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook絕不希望平台被人們用作操縱他人之用，因此會持續偵測並制止這類行為出現。Facebook刪除這些專頁、群組和帳戶是基於他們的行為，而並非因為他們的帖文內容。這些活動背後的人士互相聯繫，並利用假帳戶建立不真實的身分，這些就是Facebook採取行動的原因。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook在阻止這類行為上已取得若干進展。然而，如Facebook之前所提及，這是一項持續的挑戰。Facebook承諾將在這方面繼續努力，建立更優秀的技術、招聘更多員工，並與執法機構、安全專家和其他企業緊密合作。<br />\n<br />\n以下是被移除專頁曾發佈的一些內容：<br />\n<img src=\"https://fbnewsroomus.files.wordpress.com/2019/08/image-5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbnewsroomus.files.wordpress.com%2F2019%2F08%2Fimage-5.png&h=01bfa027&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fbnewsroomus.files.wordpress.com/2019/08/image-1-2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbnewsroomus.files.wordpress.com%2F2019%2F08%2Fimage-1-2.png&h=97f4af77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fbnewsroomus.files.wordpress.com/2019/08/image-2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbnewsroomus.files.wordpress.com%2F2019%2F08%2Fimage-2.png&h=0b7aa93e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fbnewsroomus.files.wordpress.com/2019/08/image-1-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbnewsroomus.files.wordpress.com%2F2019%2F08%2Fimage-1-1.png&h=197ba894&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fbnewsroomus.files.wordpress.com/2019/08/image-4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbnewsroomus.files.wordpress.com%2F2019%2F08%2Fimage-4.png&h=cd15a0b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2386c932f863e4568a4ffde24cc6a4e9f93f51ae","tid":1490589,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:04:48.000Z","msg":"無港人港地？"},{"pid":"49f0b41356a685e73564a25d08a8df16818a7d00","tid":1490589,"uid":302596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:04:50.000Z","msg":"繼續打擊五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2756b702e05959cf5e9c6f4d63bdc8506c584647","tid":1490589,"uid":67816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:05:04.000Z","msg":"得7個專頁、3個群組和5個帳戶都拎出黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee03387c8ee7825a083e51ea6d345221b9f9ae7d","tid":1490589,"uid":302596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2386c932f863e4568a4ffde24cc6a4e9f93f51ae","tid":1490589,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:04:48.000Z","msg":"無港人港地？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:05:37.000Z","msg":"依啲藍絲頁好大機會係班建制係香港開出黎"},{"pid":"eb90b815b06c35f765444e85680a096f46717436","tid":1490589,"uid":169079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2756b702e05959cf5e9c6f4d63bdc8506c584647","tid":1490589,"uid":67816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:05:04.000Z","msg":"得7個專頁、3個群組和5個帳戶都拎出黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"